      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. Honestly, it\u2019s in incredible shape\u2014totally spotless inside and out, and it drives like an absolute dream! It has been pampered since day one and is looking for a new home where it'll be just as loved. You really have to see it in person to believe how fresh it still feels. It\u2019s basically like driving it off the lot for the first time! Feel free to reach out with any questions, I'm super happy to chat!",
      "price": 43500.0,
