    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in collector condition. This S54-powered masterpiece features a high-pressure VANOS system that has been fully overhauled with Beisan components, ensuring optimal cam timing and zero rattle. The 3.2L atmospheric straight-six breathes through individual throttle bodies, delivering a linear power band to the 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis is structurally flawless; the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with VinceBar plates to mitigate fatigue. Power is managed by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Every bushing has been replaced with OEM+ polyurethane for razor-sharp turn-in. Original paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior retains its factory matte finish with no bolster wear. A mechanically perfect example for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
